.BR hpacucli (8),
.BR hpacuxe (8),

.UR http://cciss.sf.net
.UE ,
and
.I Documentation/blockdev/cciss.txt
and
.I Documentation/ABI/testing/sysfs-bus-pci-devices-cciss
in the Linux kernel source tree
